data.description: Amazing duplex in the much-desired Cambridge Heights neighborhood of Red Lion. Upon entering the house, the main level has a spacious living room, the dining room area leads to the beautiful two-tier deck overlooking the backyard and large side yard. There's plenty of kitchen counter space along with a moveable island. The half bath and laundry room are conveniently located on the main level. The upper level has 3 spacious bedrooms and a full bath with a walk-in closet in the main bedroom. The lower level has a fully finished den and a large family room with a built-in bar.
